com.facebook.litho.testing.logging

Class TestComponentsLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.testing.logging.TestComponentsLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentsLogger

    public class TestComponentsLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements ComponentsLogger
    In test environments we don't want to recycle the events as mockity hold on to them. We therefor override log() to not call release.
